pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `3f2da47` to `3364880`.
Commits
  • 3364880 Update windows cross-compiling toolchain and documentation [skip ci] (#959)
  • 7f30882 Manually remove fips202 files left by copy_from_upstream (#958)
  • 7a5001f Fix compilation of KeccakP-1600-AVX2.s on macOS
  • b36ff9f Replace OQS_PORTABLE_BUILD and OQS_USE_CPU_EXTENSIONS (#951)
  • See full diff in compare view
